<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Jun1927"><font color="red">4 June 1927</font> <i>Beach Letters</i> (to Sylvia Beach): Many thanks for proof and note received. Am working hard at former and will forward at once as soon as I get Miss Weaver&apos;s set. I have made many changes. </div>
